                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-239-off1313 t18280529-239-cd1314"></join>, 9 lbs. weight of horse-hair, value 35s.; 1 coat, value 10s.; 2 pairs of pantaloons, value 17s.; 1 waistcoat, value 18d.; and 1 handkerchief, value 1d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280529-239-victim1295" type="victimName">
